{"id": 2812, "genre": 1001, "title": "生活中你都有哪些“怀疑自己上了年纪”的瞬间？", "description": "一种「砰地一声意识到“哎原来自己也经历过这么多了啊”」的体验。（题图来自：iStock ️©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 5188, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190304114351xoMNgCfcP6RmYW5S.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-04T03:00:34Z", "options": [{"id": 332289, "content": "身体各种不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605874}, {"id": 331010, "content": "听“一剪梅”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418382}, {"id": 331778, "content": "看见化妆的初中生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603134}, {"id": 330756, "content": "偶然间活动关节响", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600633}, {"id": 331268, "content": "只要看见比自己年轻的人 已经做了自己很早之前做的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602025}, {"id": 332292, "content": "回家看到邻家小孩！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1606104}, {"id": 331013, "content": "查百度才知道“本可”是什么意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418382}, {"id": 330758, "content": "看到儿子的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600634}, {"id": 331014, "content": "脱发", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 51909}, {"id": 330759, "content": "被催婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475489}, {"id": 330760, "content": "给父母打去第一笔钱的时候\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587707}, {"id": 330761, "content": "几乎没有一点个人娱乐期间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600644}, {"id": 331785, "content": "年轻的时候扮成熟，现在喜欢装嫩装可爱🐶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603299}, {"id": 330762, "content": "不知道防弹少年团", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352265}, {"id": 332042, "content": "看小孩谈恋爱无感", "image": "img/option/option/201903081506224Btm9PhxAXGV0Nd3.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561248}, {"id": 330763, "content": "磁带已经变成怀旧餐厅的摆设而不是日常生活用品了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 330764, "content": "VCD已经不流行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147506}, {"id": 330765, "content": "前天开生日会开了两桌\n另一桌说他们那边都是老年人啊\n然后聊天话题 他们那边都是天南海北\n我们这边都是实习工作考研", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600647}, {"id": 330766, "content": "这些年轻人搞的新玩意真蠢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927309}, {"id": 330767, "content": "去四楼教室感觉喘", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481974}, {"id": 331535, "content": "发现新晋偶像/演员已经比我小了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467674}, {"id": 334864, "content": "下载了好奇心日报的那一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 330772, "content": "各种不认识的小鲜肉明星", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1594775}, {"id": 331284, "content": "小朋友:\"阿姨好。\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459819}, {"id": 330773, "content": "某天路过深大，我背着书包，小男孩小女孩们，也背着书包，就这样，南方傍晚的夕阳还是很刺眼，我看了眼手表，2019年3月3日。原来，我已经离开校园近4年了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596482}, {"id": 331797, "content": "小朋友叫叔叔！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603320}, {"id": 330774, "content": "一觉不能睡到9点后", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522195}, {"id": 330775, "content": "去KTV唱的还是十年前自己会唱的歌，一首新歌都没有学会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286091}, {"id": 330776, "content": "看着亲人去世", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596862}, {"id": 330777, "content": "才没有，我一直是个孩子，可我从未停止成长", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600663}, {"id": 331289, "content": "熬夜都要为自己逐渐年迈的身体想想！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 339225, "content": "我的喜欢的音乐、感兴趣的东西和身边同学完全不同，甚至和广泛的大人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637638}, {"id": 330778, "content": "年岁有加，并非垂老。理想丢弃，方堕暮年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600663}, {"id": 331802, "content": "熬夜一次要用几天时间恢复", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603345}, {"id": 330779, "content": "妈妈的一句，我老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599179}, {"id": 331036, "content": "在小孩子叫阿姨的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601363}, {"id": 331548, "content": "听到小孩叫我阿姨！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602688}, {"id": 330781, "content": "尿频了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937329}, {"id": 330784, "content": "从小崔变成了小崔哥，身边的人都开始结婚生娃，瞬间就感觉到了", "image": "img/option/option/20190304190302GdQ5DZYpPwknyNR0", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1597641}, {"id": 330785, "content": "突然觉得追求一个人很奢侈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327163}, {"id": 331297, "content": "不小心看到了照出来的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220151}, {"id": 334881, "content": "执念。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234275}, {"id": 330786, "content": "脾气温和，甚至不会生气了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146988}, {"id": 331298, "content": "真的害怕体检", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538603}, {"id": 330787, "content": "洗菜洗碗久了，会腰疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146988}, {"id": 331299, "content": "和朋友讨论别人的年龄和相貌是否符合的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220151}, {"id": 330788, "content": "约伴旅游时，发现自己是同行中年龄最大的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598588}, {"id": 330789, "content": "明星比自己小", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292442}, {"id": 338469, "content": "当朋友圈充满了晒娃狂魔的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475876}, {"id": 330790, "content": "娱乐圈流行的小鲜肉都不认识", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598726}]}